Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.94,0:38:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.94,0:38:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If divinity is ever-present, this lovingness is the field in which we operate and thrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.42,0:38:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So this lovingness, to me, God is lovingness. Lovingness and the propensity for love to go to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.17,0:38:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The propensity is for love to go to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.51,0:38:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We recently had a lecture on love, didn't we? It had to do with the propensity of love to go to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.76,0:38:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's kind of weird that here we have this Thanksgiving holiday that involves bounty, because we celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.61,0:39:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We have the harvest, basically, is how it all started.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.61,0:39:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We're thankful for our family, friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.19,0:39:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.53,0:39:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The food that we eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.55,0:39:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So the Thanksgiving holiday is a chance to really be thankful for the gifts that have been granted us.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.63,0:39:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We're surrounded by gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.63,0:39:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.98,0:39:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that we are still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.98,0:39:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I say, well, thank you, God, that I'm still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.30,0:39:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And I devote my life to the usefulness to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.78,0:39:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So that gives it some value.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.67,0:39:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Because just having things doesn't increase value.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.69,0:39:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It increases fun and pleasure, but it doesn't really increase value.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.69,0:40:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And it could be that certain lifetimes you spend more lifetimes in service, would you say, to others, rather than...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.34,0:40:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I think if you go into the historical background of many people, you'll find a certain pattern to their...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.38,0:40:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.38,0:40:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...recurrent emergence into the human life.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.38,0:40:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.67,0:40:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,To be of service or to make up for having not been of service.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.36,0:40:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.15,0:40:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you were to sum everything up as live your life like a prayer, what message would you give us?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.69,0:40:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,To be grateful for the opportunity for your own existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.69,0:40:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I always say, dear God, I'm very grateful that I exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.69,0:40:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And I consider this a gift which I treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.21,0:40:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And I will try to use this gift to the best of my ability to spread that love and gratitude to others, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.71,0:41:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So the way I express my gratitude to God is by being loving towards others to the greatest extent I can do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.13,0:41:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when they pull out in front of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.59,0:41:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's just a childish annoyance that somebody has gotten in your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.86,0:41:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.86,0:41:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.86,0:41:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.86,0:41:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,As you're racing down the highway, suddenly a car pulls out from the side of the road right in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.86,0:41:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's just very hard to take what you're saying and put it into every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.55,0:41:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's an attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.55,0:41:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And because it's an attitude, it prevails and covers all the conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.55,0:41:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So if a car is going too slow, you have one kind of response.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.96,0:41:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If the car is pulling out too fast, you have one kind of response.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.96,0:42:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But all of them are being governed by your gratitude that you have the opportunity to save people's lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.51,0:42:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to serve other people, and to be alive for the benefit of yourself and others.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.86,0:42:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So live your life like a prayer every day and in every way.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.96,0:42:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,To be grateful for your own existence and to share your appreciation to God that you exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.26,0:42:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And the opportunity to express your love towards others is a gift from God.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.63,0:42:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And I give thanks to the old Lord for the gift of being able to be here with you right now and record this event.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.63,0:42:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, dear Lord, for the chance to record this event.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.73,0:42:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And after you and I are long gone, this recording will still be available if anybody's interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.15,0:42:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Way back in the olden times.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.53,0:42:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,In the olden times.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.53,0:43:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,When old Doc Hoggins and old Susan Hoggins were still kicking around and alive, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.53,0:43:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Way, way back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.76,0:43:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be old, old, old folks before you know it, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.09,0:43:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, thank you.
